Document: CSGSphere3D
Path: godot/classes/class_csgsphere3d.rst
Summary: Properties and their default values for the CSGSphere3D class.

Property: material (Material): The material applied to the sphere. Default: none.
Property: radial_segments (int): Number of segments around the sphere's circumference. Default: 12.
Property: radius (float): The radius of the sphere. Default: 0.5.
Property: rings (int): Number of horizontal segments dividing the sphere. Default: 6.
Property: smooth_faces (bool): Enables smooth shading for the sphere's surface. Default: true.
